- **Left sidebar**: Full sport navigation list with icons, expandable competitions by sport
- **Main content area**: Events list or market view
- **Right sidebar**: Bet slip (sticky, always visible on desktop)
- **Top header**: Logo, navigation tabs (Sports, In-Play, Live Streaming, My Bets, etc.), account balance, login
