## Real-Time Behavior — Must Feel Live

- Odds must update **without page refresh** using WebSocket (Socket.io)
- When odds change: flash the button **green** if odds increased (drifted), **red** if decreased (shortened)
- Live match score must update in real time
- Bet slip potential returns must recalculate instantly when odds change while selection is in slip
- In-play event list must re-sort as events start/finish without page reload
- If a market is suspended: grey out the odds button and show "SUSP" text

---

## Cash Out Feature

- Available on eligible open bets (singles and accumulators)
- Cash Out value calculated as: `(current odds of remaining selections / original odds) × original stake`
- Full Cash Out: settle immediately at current value
- Partial Cash Out: slider to choose what percentage to cash out, remainder stays open
- Cash Out value updates in real time via WebSocket
- If market is suspended: Cash Out button disabled showing "Cash Out Unavailable"

