## External Data API Integration

Use one of these APIs for real sports data:
- **Primary recommendation**: SportRadar API (most complete, used by major bookmakers)
- **Alternative**: BetsAPI (via RapidAPI) — cheaper, good coverage
- **Alternative**: API-Football for football-only (very affordable)
- **Alternative**: The Odds API (good for odds aggregation)

The odds sync job must:
- Fetch live event odds every **5 seconds** for in-play events
- Fetch pre-match odds every **60 seconds** for upcoming events
- Cache all odds in Redis with key `odds:{eventId}:{marketType}`
- Push changes to clients via Socket.io room `event:{eventId}`
- Detect odds changes and include direction (up/down) in the WebSocket payload so frontend can flash the correct color

