## Account & Credit System (BetArena-Specific)

This is where BetArena differs from Bet365. Instead of real money deposits:

- Users have a **virtual credit balance**
- Credits are created only by Admin and distributed through the agent hierarchy
- No deposit, no withdrawal, no payment gateway
- Everything else (bet placement, settlement, balance updates) works identically to a real bookmaker

