## What This Is NOT

- Not a real money platform (no payment processing needed)
- Not a 100% pixel-perfect clone (BetArena has its own branding and minor creative differences)
- Not a casino platform in Phase 1 (slots, live casino are out of scope initially)
- Not a live streaming platform (no video rights — show stats/tracker instead)

---

## Summary

When in doubt: **open bet365.com, look at how they did it, build it that way.**

The goal is that a Bet365 user sitting down at BetArena feels completely at home — same navigation logic, same bet slip behavior, same markets, same bet types — just with a different color scheme and logo, and virtual credits instead of real money.
